# shadcn/ui Quick Setup Commands

## Initial Setup (if not already installed)
```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Common Component Installation Commands

### Essential Components
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
npx shadcn@latest add card
npx shadcn@latest add input
npx shadcn@latest add form
```

### Layout & Navigation
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add navigation-menu
npx shadcn@latest add separator
npx shadcn@latest add tabs
npx shadcn@latest add sheet
```

### Feedback & Alerts
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add alert
npx shadcn@latest add toast
npx shadcn@latest add progress
npx shadcn@latest add badge
```

### Overlays & Dialogs
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add dialog
npx shadcn@latest add popover
npx shadcn@latest add dropdown-menu
npx shadcn@latest add tooltip
```

### Data Display
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add table
npx shadcn@latest add accordion
npx shadcn@latest add collapsible
npx shadcn@latest add avatar
```

### Form Components
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add checkbox
npx shadcn@latest add radio-group
npx shadcn@latest add select
npx shadcn@latest add textarea
npx shadcn@latest add switch
npx shadcn@latest add slider
```

## Install Multiple Components at Once
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button card input form dialog toast
```

## Check Available Components
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add
```

Use these commands in the terminal whenever you need to add new shadcn/ui components to the project.
